    <title>Materials and methods</title>
    <sec>
      <title>Statistical methods</title>
      <p>This section is devoted to describing the methodological aspects of the causal mediation analysis methods. We describe only the conceptual ideas and terms to help our users to easily understand them, while referencing the original papers for all technical details.</p>
